title: The Giaour
creator: Lord Byron
description: LibriVox recording of The Giaour, by Lord Byron. Read by Grant Hurlock. "The Giaour" is a poem by Lord Byron first published in 1813 and the first in the series of his Oriental romances. "The Giaour" proved to be a great success when published, consolidating Byron's reputation critically and commercially. (Summary by Wikipedia) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format in Grab Bag 05
subject: Librivox;audiobook;poetry;adventure;romance
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
